      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十二月二十四日　深夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "五、四、三、二、一……！　おたん……！\nっとと……お誕生日おめでとう、琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.5333333691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、渚。けど、わざわざ部屋まで来なくても\n良かったのに。朝からお仕事あるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 22.5333340049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、一番にお祝いしたかったんだもん\n昔は、琴乃ちゃんの方から遊びに来てくれたのにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.1333340049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……？　いつの話？\nあ……もしかして、中学の頃の――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.216667084
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.216667084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、今日、商店街の方を通って帰らない？\nもうすぐクリスマスだから、飾りつけされてるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.0333337506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。まぁ、いいけど\n伊吹さんって、イルミネーションとか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3666688641
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "なーぎーさ！　『伊吹さん』は禁止。もう、琴乃ちゃん\nってば、そろそろ慣れてほしいんだけどな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3000009259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなこと言われたって、慣れないことってある\nでしょ。ママから、お母さん、に呼び方変える時とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6333368024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "え～！？　琴乃ちゃんってちっちゃい頃\nママって呼んでたんだ！　可愛いっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7011853077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1000034691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないでよ！　はぁ……分かったわ\n出来るだけ、呼ぶようにするから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、まだ夕方だから、今一つだなぁ\nそういえば琴乃ちゃんはクリスマスの予定とかあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3666721702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……うん、まぁ。私、二十五日が誕生日なんだ\n一応、今のところは……家族と過ごす…………かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9666721702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "凄い！　クリスマスがお誕生日なんだね！　早く言って\nくれればいいのに～。プレゼント、二つ用意しなきゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.9333388369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、そっかぁ。家族と過ごすんだよね\nじゃあ私も、家でのんびり過ごそうかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.2666721702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_53_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかしたら、暇になるかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2666721702,
